milestones.description: Dean Minors and Clay Smith's 79-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 50 between Dean Minors and Clay Smith
Dean Minors and Romaine's 80-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 30 between Dean Minors and Steven Outerbridge
David Hemp and Lionel Cann's 75-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 52 between Romaine and Mukuddem
Porterfield and Kenny Carroll's 78-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Jeremy Bray and Porterfield
Kevin O'Brien and Porterfield's 88-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 23 between Jeremy Bray and Kevin O'Brien
Porterfield has become the top scorer for IRE in ODIs with 182 runs, going past Jeremy Bray's 146
Johnston has broken the record for most sixes (6) in ODIs for IRE, going past Jeremy Bray's 4
Mukuddem has broken the record for most catches (6) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Hasan Durham's 5
Kevin O'Brien and Porterfield's 88-run partnership is IRE's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 80 between Eoin Morgan and Niall O'Brien
Malachi Jones has broken the record for most catches in an innings (3) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Leverock's 2
Kevin O'Brien has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for IRE, going past Johnston's 3
Mukuddem has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (14) for BMUDA, going past Romaine
Andre Botha has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for IRE, going past Jeremy Bray
Dean Minors has scored 3 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for BMUDA breaking Romaine's record
